data.description: Home for the holidays! Come check out this Beautiful home very close to the Bakersfield College. This home features 4 bedrooms, 2 baths with granite countertops in kitchen, vinyl & tile flooring throughout, spacious bedrooms, indoor laundry room that leads out to the 1 car garage.  Take a look at the backyard so much room for a pool, patio, gazebo and much more! Call for a private showing!
